com.cube.storm

Class MessageSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cube.storm.MessageSettings

  • public class MessageSettings
extends Object
    This is the entry point class of the library. To enable the use of the library, you must instantiate a new MessageSettings.Builder object in your Application singleton class. This class should not be directly instantiated.
